WEBVTT

00:06.590 --> 00:07.260
- Previously, on "Happy!"...

00:08.660 --> 00:09.830
- Why don't you tell me
where we're going?

00:09.860 --> 00:10.830
- How the heck should I know?

00:10.860 --> 00:12.500
You're the detective.

00:12.530 --> 00:13.700
- What about the guy?
Tell me about the guy.

00:13.730 --> 00:15.170
Can you describe him?

00:15.200 --> 00:16.500
You're gonna tell me
what he looks like,

00:16.530 --> 00:17.670
I'm gonna tell him,
he's gonna draw it.

00:17.700 --> 00:18.800
- You owe me.

00:18.840 --> 00:20.540
- I don't owe you
anything at all.

00:20.570 --> 00:22.070
- The only man you ever
loved broke up his marriage.

00:22.110 --> 00:23.410
- I get it.

00:23.440 --> 00:25.340
- Father gunned down
in the line of duty.

00:25.380 --> 00:27.440
Your mother loses her mind.

00:27.480 --> 00:29.450
- I bring you Sax,
and we're even.

00:29.480 --> 00:32.280
These came from the parents
of the other missing children.

00:32.320 --> 00:33.550
Any cop worth his shit

00:33.580 --> 00:35.290
might go out there,
stake him out.

00:35.320 --> 00:36.520
- See if they get a card.

00:36.550 --> 00:38.160
- You gotta talk
to Mrs. Claws.

00:38.190 --> 00:39.690
- Reminds me of
a fella we all knew.

00:39.720 --> 00:42.330
Worked at Gimbels
before it closed down,

00:42.360 --> 00:43.630
ended up hanging himself.

00:43.660 --> 00:45.700
- My monster is very much
alive and kicking.

00:45.730 --> 00:49.670
- Not him, his son.

00:52.600 --> 00:55.440
- You look just
like your picture.

00:57.370 --> 00:58.610
- Nick, are you all right?

00:58.640 --> 01:00.480
Oh no.

01:00.510 --> 01:02.350
- I can see you.

01:07.250 --> 01:11.260
No, no, please.

01:11.290 --> 01:13.890
You.

01:18.660 --> 01:20.700
- But you--
you can't touch me

01:20.730 --> 01:22.230
unless you believe in me.

01:29.370 --> 01:31.310
Bye bye.

01:31.340 --> 01:34.380
Oh, God, no, no.

01:36.180 --> 01:38.920
- No...Happy.

